promptTemplate:
Analyze this code file and provide technical documentation in JSON format. Focus on:

1. Extract all functions and their parameters
2. Identify classes and their methods
3. Document key variables and constants
4. Create a mermaid flowchart showing the code structure
5. Generate a summary of the code's purpose

File: {{filename}}
Code:
{{code}}

Respond ONLY with valid JSON in this exact format:
{
  "summary": "Brief description of the code's purpose",
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "functionName",
      "parameters": ["param1", "param2"],
      "description": "What this function does",
      "returnType": "string|object|number|etc"
    }
  ],
  "classes": [
    {
      "name": "ClassName",
      "methods": ["method1", "method2"],
      "description": "What this class does"
    }
  ],
  "variables": [
    {
      "name": "variableName",
      "type": "string|object|number|etc",
      "description": "What this variable stores"
    }
  ],
  "mermaidDiagram": "flowchart TD\n    A[Start] --> B[Process]\n    B --> C[End]",
  "keyInsights": ["Important point 1", "Important point 2"]
}
